Budget,Your,Trip,is,a,service,that,determines,travel,costs,based,on,travel,expenses,from,actual,travelers,Users,register,on,the,site,for,free,and,enter,expenses,by,category,and,location,The,travel,expenses,are,averaged,and,aggregated,to,get,typical,travel,costs,for,destinations,around,the,world,The,new,version,of,the,API,provides,this,travel,cost,data,similar,to,what,is,displayed,on,the,website,as,well,as,currency,conversion,and,location,information